## 13. Before Commit Checklist

- [ ] `make lint` passes
- [ ] `make test` passes
- [ ] Coverage ≥80% (≥90% for critical modules)
- [ ] Docker builds (`make docker-build`)
- [ ] Commit message follows format: `<scope>: <description>`

---

## 14. Before PR Checklist

- [ ] Title: `<scope>: <description>`
- [ ] ≤500 lines, ≤10 files
- [ ] Tests included
- [ ] Documentation updated (if API changed)
- [ ] No breaking changes (or migration path provided)

